skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: go singapore
des:
Ask for Singapore Tourist places, world famous eateries (popularly known as hawker centers) and Historical Sites in Singapore

Singapore Places to Visit is an easy way to know about the world famous places in & around Singapore

To start, just say "Alexa, launch go singapore" or "Alexa, open go singapore" to get a famous tourist site info".

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
